title: Under Armour Border Patrol | Jackson, WY
description:
UA MTN athletes Kyle Clancy, Bjorn Leines, and Tyler Nicholson head from the backcountry to a quick rail jam in the variety of terrain that Jackson has to offer. 

Music – 
L.A. Witch – “Get Lost” 
Digital Leather – “The Assault”
